<TITLE> 1400 college teachers to get promotion </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Jun 3 (bdnews24.com)The government has decided to promote some 1,400 college teachers of the general education cadre. Acting director general of the Directorate of Secondary and Higher Education, Prof Noman Ur Rashid, said a meeting of the education ministry's promotion committee finalised the postings on Wednesday. The 1,400 teachers include some 700 lecturers, some 600 assistant professors and some 125 associate professors, an official of the directorate said. bd
